            <h3 class="philosophy__item__title">
                Values
            </h3>
            <div class="philosophy__items-detail__blocks">
                <div class="philosophy__item__info">
                    <h4 class="philosophy__item__info__title">
                        We work in an orderly manner
                    </h4>
                    <p class="philosophy__item__info__text">
                        We are adherents of smart management with consistent planning. We have a transparent progress
                        plan in our hands, which allows us to optimize work regularly and make deadlines safe and
                        achievable.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="philosophy__item__info">
                    <h4 class="philosophy__item__info__title">
                        We choose cooperation
                    </h4>
                    <p class="philosophy__item__info__text">
                        We appreciate working with intelligent, well-organized people in an atmosphere of cooperation
                        and trust. The ideal approach for us is balanced communication and equal involvement in the
                        project. We discuss with the client progress made, milestones achieved, issues faced and
                        resolutions elaborated.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="philosophy__item__info">
                    <h4 class="philosophy__item__info__title">
                        We care about the present
                    </h4>
                    <p class="philosophy__item__info__text">
                        Alternative energy is not an innovation of the future, it already makes the present sustainable.
                        It is important for us not only to reduce the burden on nature in our work, but also to be a
                        guide to Â«greenÂ» functioning for our clients.
                    </p>
                </div>
